<a href="/articles/27218.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27218/indexMediumPc2/27218.jpg?1463990611" alt="剑桥大学要为领袖开商科博士课程，会是个噱头吗？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/5/medium/5.png?1411569637" alt="城市">
			<span>城市</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">剑桥大学要为领袖开商科博士课程，会是个噱头吗？</h1>
	</div>
